text: The canton of Digne-les-Bains-1 is an administrative division of the Alpes-de- Haute-Provence department, in southeastern France. It was created at the French canton reorganisation which came into effect in March 2015. Its seat is in Digne-les-Bains. It consists of the following communes: #Le Castellard- Mélan #Digne-les-Bains (partly) #Entrages #Hautes-Duyes #Marcoux #La Robine- sur-Galabre #Thoard ==References== Category:Cantons of Alpes-de-Haute-Provence
title: Canton of Digne-les-Bains-1
